sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend as React SPA
    participant Backend as FastAPI
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    actor Owner as Data Owner

    User->>Frontend: View retrieval results
    Frontend-->>User: species ranking displayed
    User->>Frontend: Submit feedback / contribution
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/v1/feedback
    Backend->>DB: INSERT feedback (status=pending)
    DB-->>Backend: feedback_id
    Backend-->>Frontend: 201 Created
    Frontend-->>User: Feedback submitted

    Owner->>Frontend: Open feedback inbox
    Frontend->>Backend: GET /api/v1/feedback/inbox
    Backend->>DB: SELECT feedback (pending)
    DB-->>Backend: feedback list
    Backend-->>Frontend: pending feedback items
    Frontend-->>Owner: Review queue displayed

    Owner->>Frontend: Approve / reject / request edit
    Frontend->>Backend: PATCH /api/v1/feedback/inbox/{id}
    Backend->>DB: UPDATE feedback status + review_note
    DB-->>Backend: updated
    Backend-->>Frontend: review result
    Frontend-->>Owner: Review complete

    Owner->>Frontend: Approve contribution → index
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/v1/index (from feedback)
    Backend->>DB: UPDATE species / media metadata
    Backend-->>Frontend: reference updated
    Frontend-->>Owner: Contribution accepted
